relationships.description: Workspace groups can be located in specific regions, such as US West 2 (Oregon).
Workspace groups can configure firewall ranges using IP addresses.
Workspace groups can use identifiers such as KMS Key IDs for data and backup buckets.
Workspace groups generate metrics related to their performance and usage.
Workspace groups support private connections for secure communication.
Clients interact with workspace groups for management and configuration tasks.
